1388
01:16:29,703 --> 01:16:32,080
Help me, please.

1389
01:16:32,080 --> 01:16:33,123
Please.

1390
01:16:35,959 --> 01:16:36,877
Drat.

1391
01:16:36,877 --> 01:16:38,461
The fair is
resuming, and here we

1392
01:16:38,461 --> 01:16:41,131
are guarding this one
who's as good as dead.

1393
01:16:41,131 --> 01:16:43,717
You took the words
right out of my mouth.

1394
01:16:43,717 --> 01:16:46,344
And I've got an idea.

1395
01:16:46,344 --> 01:16:49,139
You go along and
enjoy the fair.

1396
01:16:49,139 --> 01:16:50,641
I'll stay guard.

1397
01:16:50,641 --> 01:16:52,893
No use both of us missing out.

1398
01:16:52,893 --> 01:16:56,563
You come back later,
and we'll switch.

1399
01:16:56,563 --> 01:16:59,191
I don't know.

1400
01:16:59,191 --> 01:17:00,067
Look.

1401
01:17:00,067 --> 01:17:01,819
No one will know.

1402
01:17:01,819 --> 01:17:02,986
You say nothing, and--

1403
01:17:02,986 --> 01:17:04,822
Say no more.

1404
01:17:04,822 --> 01:17:07,240
Whoopee!

1405
01:17:07,240 --> 01:17:09,242
I'll see you soon!

1406
01:17:09,242 --> 01:17:12,746
[TENSE MUSIC]

1407
01:17:16,208 --> 01:17:16,709
Huh?

1408
01:17:42,109 --> 01:17:45,612
[FOREBODING MUSIC]

1409
01:17:47,614 --> 01:17:50,075
[FOOTSTEPS]

1410
01:18:01,086 --> 01:18:02,587
[TENSE DRAMATIC MUSIC]

1411
01:18:02,587 --> 01:18:05,090
Ah!

1412
01:18:05,090 --> 01:18:06,091
No!

1413
01:18:06,091 --> 01:18:07,634
Please!

1414
01:18:07,634 --> 01:18:09,469
