I cannot go back.

1428
01:18:50,969 --> 01:18:53,596
And so you shall go with me.

1429
01:18:53,596 --> 01:18:55,348
But I just realized,

1430
01:18:55,348 --> 01:18:58,393
I do not yet know your name.

1431
01:18:58,393 --> 01:19:00,312
Hopeful.

1432
01:19:00,312 --> 01:19:02,314
Hopeful.

1433
01:19:02,314 --> 01:19:06,819
Then, rest tonight, as your
name implies, brave Hopeful.

1434
01:19:06,819 --> 01:19:09,612
For tomorrow, we
journey on to our King.

1435
01:19:09,612 --> 01:19:13,075
[GENTLE MUSIC]

