[SNORING]

1506
01:23:55,690 --> 01:23:58,318
What happened?

1507
01:23:58,318 --> 01:24:01,113
Did he just faint?

1508
01:24:01,113 --> 01:24:02,489
Not again.

1509
01:24:02,489 --> 01:24:05,117
Oh, dear.

1510
