1593
01:28:09,361 --> 01:28:11,363
[TENSE DRAMATIC MUSIC]

1594
01:28:11,363 --> 01:28:13,323
[SHOUT]

1595
01:28:15,325 --> 01:28:15,825
Quickly.

1596
01:28:24,250 --> 01:28:27,712
You get them, cherry lips!

1597
01:28:27,712 --> 01:28:30,715
