1598
01:28:30,715 --> 01:28:34,719
Get back here!

1599
01:28:34,719 --> 01:28:36,721
[HOPEFUL AND CHRISTIAN SHOUT]

1600
01:28:36,721 --> 01:28:38,640
That's good, dear.

1601
01:28:38,640 --> 01:28:40,975
You're doing very well.

1602
01:28:40,975 --> 01:28:46,356
Really, very well, you
good-for-nothing oaf.

1603
01:28:48,566 --> 01:28:49,567
Oh, dear.

1604
01:28:52,570 --> 01:28:54,864
[GIANT PANTING]

1605
01:28:54,864 --> 01:28:55,823
Quickly.

1606
01:28:59,452 --> 01:29:02,204
Get them, you blithering fool!

